DD_Attribute.definition:
The particle_spectral_range_min parameter define the lower bound of the spectral domain 
            for particles. Depending on the particle_spectral_type parameter, this quantity is expressed on an energy, 
            mass, or mass/charge scale, with respective units eV, amu, or amu/qe.

The particle_spectral_range_max parameter define the upper bound of the spectral domain 
            for particles. Depending on the particle_spectral_type parameter, this quantity is expressed on an energy, 
            mass, or mass/charge scale, with respective units eV, amu, or amu/qe.
